title: IndyCar Series - 2014 Honda Indy 200 at Mid-Ohio [720p / DUAL AU
description:
That's Round 15 of Verizon IndyCar Series held in Lexington, Mid-Ohio. Assuming there are people who haven't watched the race LIVE, I won't say a word this time about what happened in this race due to some complaints :) Speaking of which, I wanna apologize for spoilers on previous torrents. 

This race is the first one that I added Dual Audio feature as I could get English commentaries before. That's why I took a bit longer to upload it. So, on 1st audio track it's Brazilian Portuguese Commentaries (Nivaldo Prieto and Felipe Giafonne) while on the 2nd audio track it's NBC Sport Network commetaries (who takes part in NBC sports coverage crew, by the way?). Audio sync is not that perfect because of the instability of cable TV provider signal in some parts of the race but I did my best. Just in case of 2nd audio track being mute for two or three minutes every now and then, it's because of U.S. COMMERCIAL BRAKES :) - In Brazil there is NO COMMERCIAL BRAKES during the race. Video feed is provided by BandSports, a Grupo Bandeirantes's channel. Please, comment below of what you've thought of English track and sync.
